<h3>Pingry COVID-19 Update</h3>
<h5>A change has been noted on your isolation status.</h5>
<hr/>

<p>Dear <%= "#{@student.first_name} #{@student.last_name}"%>,</p>

<p>According to Pingry's records, you are currently in an isolation period after receiving a presumed or confirmed positive diagnosis for COVID-19. Thank you for your recent update on your isolation status. We are happy to hear you are feeling better.</p>

<p>If there are any additional updates to your isolation status, please contact <a href="mailto:contacttracing@pingry.org">contacttracing@pingry.org</a>.</p>

<p>Thank you for your partnership as we work to keep Pingry safe!</p>

Your Current Isolation Status: 
<ul>
    <li>Start: <%= @isolation.start_isolation %></li>
    <li>Date of Symptom Improvement: <%= @isolation.date_improving || "Not Yet Improving" %></li>
    <li><%= @isolation.confirmed ? "Confirmed Positive" : "Presumed Positive" %> </li>
    <li>Fever Free? <%= @isolation.fever_free ? "Yes" : "No"%></li>
    <li>Earliest Possible End Date: <%= @isolation.end_date || "Not Listed" %></li>
    <li>Overall Status: <%= @isolation.completed ? "Isolation Complete" : "Isolation Incomplete" %></li>
</ul>

<p>The Pingry School</p>
